                            "searchField": "printable_hole barboursmith a 3d printable hole. 3d printers struggle to print the top of round holes so this adds a gentle slope to the top of the hole making it print right. you need to orient it so that when the part is printed the point is up. ",
                            "owner": "BarbourSmith",
                            "description": "A 3D printable hole. 3D printers struggle to print the top of round holes so this adds a gentle slope to the top of the hole making it print right. You need to orient it so that when the part is printed the point is up.",
